education.com/world-university-rankings/2018/subject-ranking/business-and-economics#!/page/1/length/25/sort_by/rank/sort_order/asc/cols/stats|title=World University Rankings 2018 by subject: business and economics|date=12 September 2017|work=Times Higher Education (THE)|access-date=10 July 2018|language=en}}</ref>\n| N/A\n|-\n|[[U.S. News & World Report|US News]]\n|Best Global Universities for Economics and Business\n|\n|\n|27th<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.usnews.com/education/best-global-universities/economics-business|title=Best Global Universities for Economics and Business|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141029041122/http://www.usnews.com/education/best-global-universities/economics-business|archive-date=29 October 2014|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|24th<ref>https://www.usnews.com/education/best-global-universities/bocconi-university-502370</ref>\n|-\n|[[Bloomberg Businessweek|Bloomberg]]\n|Best International Business Schools\n|8th<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/features/2016-best-international-business-schools/|title=Bloomberg - Are you a robot?|website=www.bloomberg.com|access-date=6 October 2018}}</ref>\n|7th<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2017-best-international-business-schools/|title=These Are the Best International MBA Programs|work=Bloomberg.com|access-date=10 July 2018}}</ref>\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Forbes]]\n|The Best International MBAs: One-Year Programs\n|\n|5th<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.forbes.com/business-schools/list/international-1-year/|title=Best International MBAs: One-Year Programs|work=Forbes|access-date=13 July 2018|language=en}}</ref>\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[The Economist]]\n|MBA\n|38th\n|28th\n|24th<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.economist.com/whichmba/full-time-mba-ranking|title=2018 MBA & Business School Rankings - Which MBA?|website=The Economist}}</ref>\n|13th\n|-\n|[[University of Texas at Dallas|The UTD]]\n|Top 100 Worldwide Business School Rankings Based on Research Contributions\n|59th<ref>{{Cite 