usiness-management-studies|title=Business & Management Studies|date=2 March 2017|work=Top Universities|access-date=10 July 2018|language=en}}</ref>\n|10th<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2018/business-management-studies|title=Business & Management Studies|date=22 February 2018|work=Top Universities|access-date=10 July 2018|language=en}}</ref>\n|8th<ref name=\"topuniversities.com\"/>\n|-\n|Economics & Econometrics\n|17th<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2016/economics-econometrics|title=QS World University Rankings by Subject 2016 - Economics & Econometrics|date=17 March 2016|work=Top Universities|access-date=10 July 2018|language=en}}</ref>\n|16th<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2017/economics-econometrics|title=Economics & Econometrics|date=2 March 2017|work=Top Universities|access-date=10 July 2018|language=en}}</ref>\n|16th<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2018/economics-econometrics|title=Economics & Econometrics|date=22 February 2018|work=Top Universities|access-date=10 July 2018|language=en}}</ref>\n|16th<ref name=\"topuniversities.com\"/>\n|-\n|Global MBA\n|\n|\n|22nd<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/mba-rankings/global/2018|title=World University Rankings - Full Time MBA: Global 2018|date=23 November 2017|work=Top Universities|access-date=10 July 2018|language=en}}</ref>\n|10th<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/mba-rankings/europe/2019|title=World University Rankings - Full Time MBA: Europe 2019|date=18 September 2018|website=Top Universities}}</ref>\n|-\n|Global EMBA\n|\n|\n|19th<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.topmba.com/emba-rankings/global/2018|title=Executive MBA Rankings - Global 2018|date=20 April 2018|work=TopM